{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 723121, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "各取所需 大家不都把他当小丑看吗？", "timestamp": 1608130926, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "命名个楼算什么为所欲为 除了楼他还能影响到什么吗？", "timestamp": 1608131007, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723135, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "较大的法学院都是他命名的，我们学校有节操多。", "timestamp": 1608131056, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 最奇怪的是他对法学的投入，按理说想要证明他那一套轩辕反熵体系不应该向物理方向投钱吗", "timestamp": 1608131246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是命名楼就意味着很多，可以参考当你四教被真维斯冠名时清华同学的反应", "timestamp": 1608131299, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723171, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 问题是大家都心里把他当小丑，但还得笑脸陪着，领了廖凯原奖金还得写感谢信", "timestamp": 1608131355, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723219, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不就相当于用几千万或者几亿买一个monument嘛 吃人嘴短", "timestamp": 1608131689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723278, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人家捐了那么多钱，给他个机会让他讲讲自己那一套理论不也合情合理……", "timestamp": 1608132086, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723302, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "命个名而已，又不是宣扬他的理论。。别享受着别人捐的楼还要反过来嘲讽一下", "timestamp": 1608132285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 723306, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且我一直觉得不管是谁，民科也好专业人士也好，对学术圈感兴趣是好事，至少比只对钱感兴趣要好得多", "timestamp": 1608132308, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 724664, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一个八卦：你清法学院本来收了廖凯原的钱建楼，但廖凯原要求把他的理论写到进门门口被校领导否了，然后楼建一半（还是没建）他撤资了😅", "timestamp": 1608170018, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 726509, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 他捐了一个亿，先给了七千万，因为没谈拢剩下三千万不给了", "timestamp": 1608194954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 727152, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "紧张啥，捐资助学不是好事吗？你可以不认同他的观点，但不影响你拿他的钱做正经的学术研究啊", "timestamp": 1608202458, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 727153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 清华法学院以前是给廖开课的，领奖学金的人都要去听课。不过这课不会在选课系统中出现，想不到吧", "timestamp": 1608202461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 727154, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 150783, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有钱拿不好吗", "timestamp": 1608202489, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 150783, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "理想讨论\n清北复交收廖凯原的钱建楼并命名是不是代表着在学术界也是有钱可以为所欲为", "timestamp": 1608130896, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1608202490, "url": "", "vote": {}}}